---
title: Smart Lime Pork Tenderloin  with Guacamole-Ranch Sauce
description: Get ready to salsa into flavour town with this zesty delight: Seared pork tenderloin, marinated in tangy lime, with creamy guacamole-ranch sauce. Fresh greens and crunchy cucumbers add to the plate and make this a dinner fiesta.
